  "script": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 9.86,
      "text": "스크린 잉글리쉬"
    },
    {
      "start": 9.86,
      "end": 30.58,
      "text": "The Morning Theater Screen English Time"
    },
    {
      "start": 30.58,
      "end": 32.88,
      "text": "9월에 함께하고 있는 영화는"
    },
    {
      "start": 32.88,
      "end": 37.34,
      "text": "가을날의 감성처럼 우리의 마음을 잔잔하게 파고드는"
    },
    {
      "start": 37.34,
      "end": 38.34,
      "text": "Koda"
    },
    {
      "start": 38.34,
      "end": 40.54,
      "text": "입니다. 어서 오세요."
    },
    {
      "start": 41.04,
      "end": 42.04,
      "text": "Hey there, good morning."
    },
    {
      "start": 42.46,
      "end": 43.76,
      "text": "Good morning 입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 43.76,
      "end": 46.8,
      "text": "그러고 보니까 the holidays were already gone."
    },
    {
      "start": 47.04,
      "end": 48.26,
      "text": "They flew by."
    },
    {
      "start": 48.4,
      "end": 51.52,
      "text": "Yeah, I'm sure probably there are some people who feel bad."
    },
    {
      "start": 51.64,
      "end": 53.26,
      "text": "It's gone already."
    },
    {
      "start": 53.56,
      "end": 55.14,
      "text": "Time to go back to reality."
    },
    {
      "start": 55.28,
      "end": 55.6,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 55.74,
      "end": 56.54,
      "text": "Back to work."
    },
    {
      "start": 56.76,
      "end": 61.34,
      "text": "다시 일상으로 복귀하는 게 생각보다 좀 쉽지는 않을 거예요."
    },
    {
      "start": 61.46,
      "end": 61.66,
      "text": "그죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 61.9,
      "end": 62.2,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 62.56,
      "end": 65.68,
      "text": "아쉬운 마음이 있으신 분들도 물론 계시겠지만"
    },
    {
      "start": 65.68,
      "end": 69.3,
      "text": "우리가 계속해서 Koda에 빠져들어 보는 거죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 69.42,
      "end": 70.06,
      "text": "Don't worry."
    },
    {
      "start": 70.06,
      "end": 70.72,
      "text": "We have Koda."
    },
    {
      "start": 71.1,
      "end": 71.34,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 71.44,
      "end": 73.36,
      "text": "Chuseok is over but we have Koda still."
    },
    {
      "start": 73.56,
      "end": 75.12,
      "text": "Oh, rhyme 좋은데요."
    },
    {
      "start": 76.04,
      "end": 81.96,
      "text": "저는 개인적으로 이 Koda 등장인물 중에 누굴 제일 좋아하는지 추측하실 수 있겠죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 82.32,
      "end": 84.14,
      "text": "Yes, I think I can guess."
    },
    {
      "start": 84.5,
      "end": 87.44,
      "text": "You don't like the young handsome man, Miles."
    },
    {
      "start": 87.82,
      "end": 88.5,
      "text": "그러게 말입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 88.84,
      "end": 90.64,
      "text": "I don't know why but he's not your type."
    },
    {
      "start": 90.64,
      "end": 92.76,
      "text": "Yeah, 취향이 좀 독특한가 봐요."
    },
    {
      "start": 93.02,
      "end": 94.12,
      "text": "You like funny guys."
    },
    {
      "start": 94.24,
      "end": 94.6,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 94.88,
      "end": 95.74,
      "text": "Oh, that's important."
    },
    {
      "start": 96.06,
      "end": 97.74,
      "text": "You like 아재 개그 하는 guys."
    },
    {
      "start": 97.88,
      "end": 98.72,
      "text": "Like your husband."
    },
    {
      "start": 99.1,
      "end": 99.58,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 99.84,
      "end": 102.2,
      "text": "아재 개그에 진짜 빵빵 터지다 보니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 102.2,
      "end": 105.54,
      "text": "이 영화에서는 베르나르도 선생님한테"
    },
    {
      "start": 105.54,
      "end": 107.06,
      "text": "I got attached to him."
    },
    {
      "start": 107.22,
      "end": 109.4,
      "text": "The 대표 아재 of this movie."
    },
    {
      "start": 109.6,
      "end": 109.86,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 110.1,
      "end": 110.92,
      "text": "The music teacher."
    },
    {
      "start": 110.92,
      "end": 124.82,
      "text": "Actually, believe it or not, they made another version of this movie."
    },
    {
      "start": 125.14,
      "end": 128.58,
      "text": "It's the same movie but they dubbed it in Spanish."
    },
    {
      "start": 128.8,
      "end": 133.8,
      "text": "So they got all the voice actors to dub the different parts."
    },
    {
      "start": 133.8,
      "end": 138.02,
      "text": "And this character, your favorite character,"
    },
    {
      "start": 138.44,
      "end": 141.94,
      "text": "he dubbed his own voice because he's a native Spanish speaker."
    },
    {
      "start": 142.14,
      "end": 143.4,
      "text": "Yeah, Mexican이니까."
    },
    {
      "start": 143.54,
      "end": 146.36,
      "text": "Yeah, Eugenio Derbez dubbed his own voice."
    },
    {
      "start": 146.44,
      "end": 149.98,
      "text": "So he is the same man in the Spanish version of the film."
    },
    {
      "start": 150.04,
      "end": 150.58,
      "text": "Oh, cool."
    },
    {
      "start": 151.24,
      "end": 153.34,
      "text": "I should have learned Spanish."
    },
    {
      "start": 153.6,
      "end": 154.28,
      "text": "좀 아쉽네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 154.36,
      "end": 154.62,
      "text": "Hola."
    },
    {
      "start": 155.22,
      "end": 156.8,
      "text": "Hola, 이것도 있고 또."
    },
    {
      "start": 156.94,
      "end": 157.38,
      "text": "Como estas?"
    },
    {
      "start": 157.86,
      "end": 158.6,
      "text": "Que esto?"
    },
    {
      "start": 159.02,
      "end": 159.58,
      "text": "Que esto?"
    },
    {
      "start": 159.78,
      "end": 161.1,
      "text": "Oh, 무슨 이름인지 혹시 아세요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 161.1,
      "end": 163.14,
      "text": "Is that like, what's up?"
    },
    {
      "start": 163.14,
      "end": 164.44,
      "text": "Oh, what is this?"
    },
    {
      "start": 164.56,
      "end": 165.18,
      "text": "What is this?"
    },
    {
      "start": 165.3,
      "end": 165.5,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 165.72,
      "end": 165.96,
      "text": "Oh."
    },
    {
      "start": 166.36,
      "end": 168.12,
      "text": "아기들이 좋아하는 질문이잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 168.36,
      "end": 169.06,
      "text": "Que esto?"
    },
    {
      "start": 169.32,
      "end": 170.0,
      "text": "Que esto?"
    },
    {
      "start": 170.4,
      "end": 170.98,
      "text": "이건 뭐야?"
    },
    {
      "start": 171.22,
      "end": 171.76,
      "text": "저건 뭐야?"
    },
    {
      "start": 172.0,
      "end": 173.22,
      "text": "계속 물어보는 거."
    },
    {
      "start": 173.34,
      "end": 174.7,
      "text": "Oh, where did you hear that one?"
    },
    {
      "start": 174.94,
      "end": 176.26,
      "text": "그냥 한번 찾아봤어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 176.38,
      "end": 179.16,
      "text": "우리 베르나르도 선생님을 좋아하는 마음으로다가."
    },
    {
      "start": 179.48,
      "end": 180.34,
      "text": "Oh, muy bueno."
    },
    {
      "start": 180.6,
      "end": 181.64,
      "text": "Yeah, 몰라요."
    },
    {
      "start": 181.84,
      "end": 182.16,
      "text": "Hola."
    },
    {
      "start": 182.74,
      "end": 185.32,
      "text": "자, 오늘 장면 먼저 듣고 오겠습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 186.35,
      "end": 188.85,
      "text": "That's the third time you're late."
    },
    {
      "start": 188.85,
      "end": 190.29,
      "text": "It's only 20 minutes."
    },
    {
      "start": 190.71,
      "end": 192.09,
      "text": "I don't care if it's one minute."
    },
    {
      "start": 192.09,
      "end": 194.91,
      "text": "It shows me that you don't respect me or my time."
    },
    {
      "start": 195.23,
      "end": 196.81,
      "text": "I have a lot going on."
    },
    {
      "start": 196.93,
      "end": 197.27,
      "text": "Me too."
    },
    {
      "start": 197.67,
      "end": 197.99,
      "text": "Me too."
    },
    {
      "start": 198.07,
      "end": 200.93,
      "text": "I have a whole life that has nothing to do with you."
    },
    {
      "start": 201.31,
      "end": 204.49,
      "text": "If you waste my time, I will not work with you."
    },
    {
      "start": 204.81,
      "end": 205.07,
      "text": "Okay?"
    },
    {
      "start": 205.85,
      "end": 206.13,
      "text": "Okay."
    },
    {
      "start": 206.82,
      "end": 207.3,
      "text": "I'm sorry."
    },
    {
      "start": 207.4,
      "end": 208.24,
      "text": "It won't happen again."
    },
    {
      "start": 209.24,
      "end": 210.34,
      "text": "Oh, he sounds serious."
    },
    {
      "start": 210.76,
      "end": 212.34,
      "text": "I think he's angry at her."
    },
    {
      "start": 212.58,
      "end": 213.4,
      "text": "Very angry."
    },
    {
      "start": 213.6,
      "end": 213.88,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 213.92,
      "end": 214.8,
      "text": "He's upset."
    },
    {
      "start": 215.12,
      "end": 215.28,
      "text": "Aw."
    },
    {
      "start": 215.4,
      "end": 216.1,
      "text": "She was late."
    },
    {
      "start": 216.1,
      "end": 221.24,
      "text": "Yeah, he's been coaching Ruby, but she's always been, you know, being late."
    },
    {
      "start": 221.6,
      "end": 221.82,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 221.82,
      "end": 221.96,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 221.96,
      "end": 226.58,
      "text": "I mean, she has a pretty good excuse, but he doesn't really know her situation."
    },
    {
      "start": 226.74,
      "end": 227.0,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 227.14,
      "end": 227.9,
      "text": "Her family."
    },
    {
      "start": 228.1,
      "end": 229.5,
      "text": "She has to help her family."
    },
    {
      "start": 229.88,
      "end": 234.94,
      "text": "So, she's late again to his house, but he's coaching her at his own home."
    },
    {
      "start": 235.04,
      "end": 235.28,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 235.34,
      "end": 236.58,
      "text": "He's teaching her how to sing."
    },
    {
      "start": 236.72,
      "end": 237.82,
      "text": "굉장히 special하네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 237.82,
      "end": 243.02,
      "text": "Yeah, he's spending a lot of his own time, personal time, to help her."
    },
    {
      "start": 243.28,
      "end": 243.46,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 243.46,
      "end": 245.72,
      "text": "So, he's very upset when she comes late."
    },
    {
      "start": 245.92,
      "end": 247.34,
      "text": "Oh, no wonder he's upset."
    },
    {
      "start": 247.56,
      "end": 248.38,
      "text": "No wonder."
    },
    {
      "start": 248.54,
      "end": 250.12,
      "text": "Um, 당연히 화가 나겠죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 250.12,
      "end": 256.02,
      "text": "You would be upset if you're an English student, if you were volunteering to teach your nephew English,"
    },
    {
      "start": 256.16,
      "end": 258.42,
      "text": "and he came late every day."
    },
    {
      "start": 259.42,
      "end": 263.18,
      "text": "완전 부글부글 끓다가 어느 순간 폭발을 하게 될 것 같아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 263.3,
      "end": 263.66,
      "text": "Her."
    },
    {
      "start": 263.8,
      "end": 264.68,
      "text": "Ah, 진짜."
    },
    {
      "start": 264.86,
      "end": 265.74,
      "text": "Come on, be on time."
    },
    {
      "start": 265.92,
      "end": 266.2,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 266.2,
      "end": 267.84,
      "text": "But poor, poor, uh, what's her name?"
    },
    {
      "start": 268.1,
